_paragraph\" >A caring babysitter.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3481240/extras/22f467ad01740359a38dccd15ebc86ff.avif?t=1766042771\" width=77 height=107 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>Mirei</u></strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Protagonist's younger sister Mirei. <br>She will bully you while looking down on you from the bottom of her heart.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3481240/extras/db168f3205a89118749b7013e86e5db7.avif?t=1766042771\" width=80 height=106 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>Stepmother Caroline</u></strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Yandere mother. Loves you so much that even thinking of you leaving makes her dizzy.</p>", "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>【Story】</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3481240/extras/ba86ee69b2c094c88e3e934eb0598b7e.avif?t=1766042771\" width=600 height=386 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >I was born in a very fortunate position, with many maids in a luxurious mansion.<br>My excellent personal butler Chloe, and my gentle babysitter who always accompany me. My willful little sister Mirei and my beloved mother.<br>I had everything and my life was going smoothly and …or so I thought until that day.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >One day, the protagonist learned that the mansion he lived in was actually the mansion of a villain family.<br>His reliable father was actually a cruel warmonger. His real mother was a war widow from an invaded area. The tyrannical father seems to be invading the protagonist's hometown.</p><p class=\"bb_pa